code: import axios from"axios";export function loadClients(size,page,sort,order,search){return axios({method:"get",url:"/api/private/clients",params:{size:size,page:page,sort:sort,order:order,search:search}}).then(function(response){return response.data;}).catch(function(){return false;});}export function createNewClinet(newClient){return axios({method:"post",url:"/api/private/clients",data:newClient}).then(function(response){return response.data;}).catch(function(){return false;});}export function updateClient(clientToEdit){return axios({method:"post",url:"/api/private/clients/update",data:clientToEdit}).then(function(response){return response.data;}).catch(function(){return false;});}export function deleteClient(clientToDelete){return axios({method:"delete",url:"/api/private/clients/"+clientToDelete.id}).then(function(){return true;}).catch(function(){return false;});}
